OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMorrisons scraps 'use by'  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdate on milk in favour of  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsniff test                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Supermarket Morrisons is to scrap 'use 
OL,6, by' dates on most of its milk in a move
OL,7, it says will stop millions of pints    
OL,8, being poured down the sink.            
OL,10,FThe retailer will instead place 'best  
OL,11,Fbefore' on 90% of its own-brand milk   
OL,12,Fand encourage customers to use a sniff 
OL,13,Ftest to check quality.                 
OL,15,FRecycling charity Wrap said Morrisons  
OL,16,Fwas the first supermarket to make the  
OL,17,Fmove, which starts later this month.   
OL,19,FIan Goode, senior milk buyer at        
OL,20,FMorrisons, said it was a "bold step".  
